{"tid":832950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九龍站下午有扶手電梯暫停　往福田列車延誤","createTime":"2018-09-23T06:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:26:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9e72d832a1d8d4bb4e0d69db06c0192b57e94919","tid":832950,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"西九龍站下午有扶手電梯暫停　往福田列車延誤<br />\n2018-09-23 HKT 14:46<br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段通車。本台記者下午以乘客身分，乘搭由香港西九龍站前往福田站的列車，期間入閘及過關過程需時約15分鐘，列車較預定時間遲7分鐘開車，車程約13分鐘，列車速度一度達時速192公里。<br />\n<br />\n乘客先在B1層的離境大堂排隊進行人手實名驗票，需要出示回鄉證及車票，再用車票入閘，並前往B3層的過境限制區，辦理出入境手續，期間秩序良好，排隊過關的人不多。不少旅客在區別香港及內地口岸區的黃線拍照留念。在候車區，職員提醒乘客預早15分鐘在閘外排隊輪候上車，在開車前10分鐘才讓乘客入閘前往月台層，不少乘客上車前拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\n另外，其中一條連接抵港大堂與離港大堂層的扶手電梯下午暫停，未知是否發生故障，等候人士只可乘搭升降機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1419576-20180923.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1419576-20180923.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vTi2tvMzgm8sWSCP0n%2FUb26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d4231fea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1419576-20180923.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ac10bc72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1419576-20180923.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"058d857d9c6398e6b80e54b7bbcee9098ac198b2","tid":832950,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb6af3074ee6101ffc9bd0e4c6b4ad4f9af0b11","tid":832950,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src